End users consent to receive messages by opting in through various methods, such as texting a specific keyword to a designated number, filling out an online form with explicit agreement, providing written or electronic consent during onboarding, or managing their preferences via a mobile app. 
Consent can also be confirmed through email, where users opt in by replying or clicking a link. Each method ensures users understand the type of messages they will receive and how they can opt out at any time
